0.0.1 UNRELEASED
	Initial gnunetbib release, based on
	131da09232bd9f3d1a71d2bf35ac5c867df718f2 of anonbib.
	Adjusted the python2.7 code to pylint.
	Added support for @booklet and @conference.
	Import and overhaul of our own Drupal-based bibliography, which
	involves some hacks in place due to the BibTeX implementation
	used in anonbib and the non-standard BibTeX exports by Drupal.
	HTML templates now use HTML5.
	We now use some functions from future to work towards python2
	+ python3 support.
	individual .bib files are produced which can be downloaded
